import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Label Kaise Padhein - How to Read Food Labels | Mizan"
  description="Learn how to read and understand food nutrition labels. Decode serving sizes, ingredients, and hidden information on packaged food."
>
  <article class="py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-3xl">

      <!-- Breadcrumb -->
      <nav class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-mizan-teal">Home</a>
        <span class="mx-2">‚Ä∫</span>
        <a href="/samjho" class="hover:text-mizan-teal">Samjho</a>
        <span class="mx-2">‚Ä∫</span>
        <span class="text-gray-700">Label Padhna</span>
      </nav>

      <!-- Header -->
      <header class="mb-8">
        <span class="text-5xl">üè∑Ô∏è</span>
        <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-4 mb-2">
          Label Kaise Padhein
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-mizan-teal">How to Read Food Labels</p>
        <p class="text-gray-500 mt-2">5 min read</p>
      </header>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
          Packaged food ke peeche wala label boring lagta hai, par yahi tumhari health ka GPS hai.
          Agar sahi se padhna aa gaya, toh koi company tumhe fool nahi kar sakti.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">1. Serving Size Ka Jhol</h2>
        <div class="bg-red-critical/5 border border-red-critical/20 rounded-xl p-5 mb-6">
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">
            <strong>Sabse bada trick:</strong> Companies serving size chhota rakhti hain taaki numbers achhe lagein.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
            Example: Ek chips packet "30g serving" dikhata hai, par packet 150g ka hai.
            Tum poora khaoge, toh multiply karo 5 se!
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">2. Per 100g Dekho</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          <strong>"Per 100g"</strong> column sabse honest hai. Isse comparison easy hota hai.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-green-safe/10 border border-green-safe/30 rounded-xl p-5 my-4">
          <p class="font-medium text-green-safe mb-2">Quick Rules (per 100g):</p>
          <ul class="space-y-1 text-gray-700">
            <li>Sugar: <strong>&lt;5g</strong> = Low, <strong>&gt;15g</strong> = High</li>
            <li>Sodium: <strong>&lt;120mg</strong> = Low, <strong>&gt;600mg</strong> = High</li>
            <li>Sat Fat: <strong>&lt;1.5g</strong> = Low, <strong>&gt;5g</strong> = High</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">3. Ingredients List Ka Secret</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Ingredients <strong>descending order</strong> mein likhe hote hain ‚Äî jo pehle hai, wo sabse zyada hai.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-amber-warning/10 border border-amber-warning/30 rounded-xl p-5 mb-6">
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Agar <strong>sugar</strong> (ya uske aliases) top 3 mein hai, toh product sugar bomb hai.
            Dekho: Glucose, fructose, corn syrup, maltodextrin ‚Äî sab sugar hai!
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">4. % Daily Value</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Ye batata hai ki ek serving mein kitna % daily limit aa raha hai.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li><strong>5% ya kam</strong> = Low (achha for sodium, sugar, sat fat)</li>
          <li><strong>15% ya zyada</strong> = High (achha for protein, fiber, vitamins)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">5. "Health" Claims Ignore Karo</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Front of pack pe jo likha hai ‚Äî "Natural", "No Added Sugar", "Protein Rich" ‚Äî ye marketing hai.
          <strong>Back label</strong> hi sach batata hai.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-mizan-teal/10 border border-mizan-teal/30 rounded-xl p-6 mt-10">
          <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold text-mizan-teal mb-3">Mizan Tip</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Label confusing lage? Sirf Mizan pe product search karo ‚Äî hum sab calculate karke simple verdict de dete hain.
          </p>
          <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mt-3 text-mizan-teal hover:underline font-medium">
            Search products ‚Üí
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Navigation -->
      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200 flex justify-between">
        <a href="/samjho" class="text-mizan-teal hover:underline">‚Üê Back to Samjho</a>
        <a href="/samjho/mizan-score" class="text-mizan-teal hover:underline">Next: Mizan Score ‚Üí</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
